name: Peeking into A Tourist Shop, Bali, Indonesia, 2018
description:
Bali is one of the most heavily impacted places by Covid-19 in Indonesia. During the pandemic, lots of people in Bali lost their tourism related job and went back to agricultural jobs. Considering the Indonesian government's handling of the pandemic, the Bali we used to know is not going back soon.

Digital Photo. Dimensions: 6000x4000.
